Privacy Policy
INTRODUCTION
LocumBell care about our clients and are committed to taking care of their personal data. We safeguard your
            privacy, by keeping your personal data secure. We process personal data where we have a lawful basis to do
            so. We aim to be clear and transparent; why and how we use your personal data, and draw your attention to
            your rights as a data subject.
This Privacy Policy application is between you, the user of this website, and LocumSys Ltd, the owner and
            provider of this website LocumBell.
There are two ways of using the LocumBell platform:
The LocumBell Platform: We provide a communications platform that allows healthcare professionals to
                find and manage locum work and clients to send shifts to their direct locums, meet new locums, perform
                compliance, complete registration processes and pay locums.
Staffing Platform: we provide a software platform for clients registered on the staff Scheduling platform to
                manage their workforce, helping them to identify their resource and scheduling needs, spot trends,
                schedule rota’s and run payroll.
