Our responses may include sensitive personal data and confidential data. In certain instances we require:
That your requests are given to us in writing (including email) or are given verbally.
Details of identity are provided, including as a minimum, first name, last name, address,
                and date of birth.
We are only able to comply with requests that relate to personal data held in accessible, structured filing
                systems for which we are the data controller.
