This Privacy Policy applies only to the actions of LocumBell and users
                with respect to this website. It does not extend to any websites that
                can be accessed from this website including, but not limited to any
                links we may provide to social media websites
For purposes of the applicable Data Protection Laws, LocumBell is the
                “data controller”. This means that LocumBell determines the purposes for
                which, and the way your data is processed
